attributes.documentation:
Base Contract for a TimeLine which is a cohesive linked list of documents that creates an
immutable and immortal history. The basic principles of a Timeline is that the data it stores can 
never be altered but new timeline documents can be appended in order to build more history.
 * NOTE: Remember to update upgradeable(version) in the declaration when creating a new version
of timeline

attributes.name: Timeline
